	<h1 class="title">霍金教授怎么看人工智能？他被问了九千个问题</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/99037/small/99037.jpg?1428742661" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">钟舒婷 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-10-12 17:45:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/15975/medium/15975.png?1444639978" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


